review: Brilliant! Must. Do. More. The Siren's call beckons! Thanks for a great time!

room_title: Escape room "Sirens Song" by Suite Escape in Amarillo
review: We did both the Siren's Song and the Council over this weekend, and both were fantastic. The themes and designs were creative and immersive. We had a blast and the host is a great guy. I highly recommend trying this escape room out!
